      <ul class="lead">
        <li>
            <p class="lead">Leftmost Derivation:</p>
            <p class="lead">The process of deriving a string by expanding the leftmost non-terminal at each step is called as leftmost derivation.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
            <p class="lead">Rightmost Derivation:</p>
            <p class="lead">The process of deriving a string by expanding the rightmost non-terminal at each step is called as rightmost derivation</p>
        </li>
    </ul>

